{"tid":2141984,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"在家享受 IZ*ONE 的演唱會吧！9 月中舉行兩小時演出","createTime":"2020-08-06T05:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T07:42:22.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0336503905e734aefd1852cb2a852218502ea7ca","tid":2141984,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"去年首度開唱還推出紀錄電影的 IZ*ONE，如今也將加入線上演唱會的行列，WIZ*ONE 千萬別錯過囉！<br />\n<br />\nOff the Record 今天（6 日）宣布 IZ*ONE 將於 9 月 13 日下午 5 點（韓國時間），舉行線上演唱會《ONEIRIC THEATER》，預計帶來長達兩小時的演出。<br />\n<br />\n《ONEIRIC THEATER》以可以容納各種幻想的劇場為背景，準備由 IZ*ONE 為 WIZ*ONE 帶來各種精彩表演，創造充滿魔力的難忘時光。<br />\n<br />\n《ONEIRIC THEATER》的門票將於 11 日在 InterPark 上搶先開賣，購買後就能經由 InteraPark 提供的連結在線上直接觀賞演出，WIZ*ONE 別忘了準時購票囉！"},{"pid":"f1015739a3fce93d175c548704c5c081754dfb91","tid":2141984,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:52:33.000Z","msg":"課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ee9a5689db6c769001ce0c7f0df47f03bb93ca","tid":2141984,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:10:51.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"e793381e550b20915e1253b781e9bda7770b6a78","tid":2141984,"uid":68678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:31:02.000Z","msg":"全個娛台share 一張飛咪得"},{"pid":"643c42598b35e9a040116ac6d7784e12113da4b5","tid":2141984,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e793381e550b20915e1253b781e9bda7770b6a78","tid":2141984,"uid":68678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:31:02.000Z","msg":"全個娛台share 一張飛咪得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:34:01.000Z","msg":"G持"}